---
import ClientDashboard from '../../components/react/ClientDashboard';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
  <title>Client Intel Dashboard | Brothers Automate</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Live client intelligence dashboard. SEO rankings, keyword tracking, competitor analysis, and digital presence monitoring, all in one place.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Client Intel Dashboard | Brothers Automate">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Live client intelligence dashboard. SEO rankings, keyword tracking, competitor analysis, and digital presence monitoring, all in one place.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://brothersautomate.com/clientintel/">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="Brothers Automate">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://brothersautomate.com/logo.png">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Client Intel Dashboard | Brothers Automate">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Live client intelligence dashboard. SEO rankings, keyword tracking, competitor analysis, and digital presence monitoring.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fb;
      color: #1a202c;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .dashboard-header {
      padding: 32px 40px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .dashboard-header h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1a202c;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }
    .dashboard-header p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #718096;
    }
    .dashboard-content {
      padding: 32px 40px;
      max-width: 1400px;
    }
    .info-btn {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 150ms;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .info-btn:hover { border-color: #cbd5e0; color: #1a202c; background: #f7fafc; }
    .info-overlay {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      z-index: 1000;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .info-overlay.active { display: flex; }
    .info-modal {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      max-width: 640px;
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 85vh;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    .info-modal h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1a202c;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .info-modal .close-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 16px;
      right: 20px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: #a0aec0;
      font-size: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .source-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .source-group h3 {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #678B05;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .source-group ul {
      padding-left: 18px;
    }
    .source-group li {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #4a5568;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .source-group li strong {
      color: #1a202c;
    }
    .trust-note {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      background: #f7fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #4a5568;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .dashboard-header, .dashboard-content {
        padding-left: 20px;
        padding-right: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="dashboard-header">
    <div>
      <h1>Client Intel Dashboard</h1>
      <p>All client scan data in one place. Click a row to view details.</p>
    </div>
    <button class="info-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('info-overlay').classList.add('active')" title="How we verify data accuracy">?</button>
  </div>

  <div id="info-overlay" class="info-overlay" onclick="if(event.target===this)this.classList.remove('active')">
    <div class="info-modal" style="position:relative">
      <button class="close-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('info-overlay').classList.remove('active')">&times;</button>
      <h2>How We Verify Data Accuracy</h2>

      <div class="source-group">
        <h3>Search & Rankings</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>DataForSEO</strong>, Domain rank, keyword positions, search volumes, and traffic estimates. Pulled from Google's index in real-time, not cached.</li>
          <li><strong>Keyword difficulty</strong>, Calculated from SERP competition analysis across the top 100 results.</li>
          <li><strong>Position tracking</strong>, Exact Google SERP position for each keyword, verified per scan.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="source-group">
        <h3>Technical Performance</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Lighthouse</strong>, Performance, accessibility, and SEO scores run against the live site each scan. Desktop and mobile tested separately.</li>
          <li><strong>Site crawl</strong>, Every page crawled for 404s, missing meta descriptions, missing H1 tags, and SSL status.</li>
          <li><strong>Tech stack</strong>, CMS, frameworks, analytics, and plugins detected via domain technology analysis.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="source-group">
        <h3>Local & Reviews</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Business Profile</strong>, Rating and review count pulled from Google's business data API.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Maps</strong>, Actual Maps pack rankings for local search queries, including competitor positions.</li>
          <li><strong>Organic SERP</strong>, Real Google search results showing exact ranking position vs. competitors.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="source-group">
        <h3>Social & Brand</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Instagram & Facebook</strong>, Follower counts, post engagement, and ad activity scraped from live profiles via Apify.</li>
          <li><strong>Review platforms</strong>, Yelp, BBB, and other directory presence checked.</li>
          <li><strong>Brand mentions</strong>, Content analysis across the web for earned media and sentiment.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="source-group">
        <h3>Company Intelligence</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Leadership & hiring</strong>, Cross-referenced from LinkedIn, job boards, and public directories.</li>
          <li><strong>Revenue estimates</strong>, Derived from employee count, industry benchmarks, and public data where available.</li>
          <li><strong>Competitor discovery</strong>, Algorithmically identified from keyword overlap and SERP competition.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-note">
        <strong>Refresh frequency:</strong> Core metrics (rankings, traffic, lighthouse, reviews) update with each refresh (~$0.04, 10 seconds). Full intelligence reports (company data, social deep-dive, competitor analysis) update with a full scan (~$1.50, 10 minutes). All data is timestamped, check the History tab for exact scan dates.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="dashboard-content">
    <ClientDashboard client:load />
  </div>
</body>
</html>
